    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储与特朗普的贸易战推动美元创下 2016 年以来最佳季度表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fed-trump-trade-drives-dollar-to-best-quarter-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元有望迎来 2022 年以来最好的一个季度，由于美国经济的韧性和美联储的鹰派前景增强了其吸引力，美元本周攀升至两年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fed-trump-trade-drives-dollar-to-best-quarter-since-2016</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 15:55:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储关键通胀数据落后于预期，美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/treasuries-gain-as-key-fed-inflation-figures-trails-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于备受关注的一批通胀数据低于预期，导致交易员上调对美联储明年降息的预期，美国国债周五晚些时候脱离盘中高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/treasuries-gain-as-key-fed-inflation-figures-trails-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 14:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要：股市将迎来一个月以来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储决定明年降息时更加谨慎，市场因此动荡，美国主要股指本周有望创下 11 月中旬以来最糟糕的一周。美国国债连续第二周遭遇抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 22:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
